DialogueEditorPhaseObject.text: Hello, Fitz! Are you going to enter the Recess Race?
I think you'd be good at it! Remember to press Up to start a course!
I know it can be tough when it seems none of your peers care for you, but I support you all the way!
Great seeing you out there, Fitz! Keep it up!
Because of the garbage you're collecting, we can open new courses!
By the way, there's something special in it for you if you get 30 gold medals! Good luck!
Augh, I hope he's not doing the race.
I'll just have to avoid him, or else I'll get infected...
Don't look at him, you'll catch his ugly.
Augh, Fitz, stop bothering us. Go pick your nose in a corner!
